{"tid":2192724,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【集氣】建議改善封鎖功能","createTime":"2020-09-07T10:01:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-09T22:28:34.000Z","uid":161684,"like":85,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"b4750b16c4d4a97c7d6540b3d1db50de87f84eb5","tid":2192724,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:01:07.000Z","msg":"如果你都有稍為留意下不尋常嘅留言同用戶<br />\n相信你都會好想做到以下呢個效果：<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">1</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">封鎖時</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YrdK02G.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYrdK02G.png&h=ee872990&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n輕鬆Log低有問題用戶嘅回覆<br />\n以及日後可以搵返當初個留言<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且原因字數不再限於三十字<br />\n<strong><span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">2</span></span></strong> <br />\n<strong><span class=\"large\">封鎖後</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KwtSqum.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKwtSqum.png&h=cf64d6fe&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n唔記得點解block咗？<br />\n可以一鍵搵返封鎖原因 <br />\n唔洗離開主題頁去搵封鎖名單<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n喺目前連登備受滲透嘅情況下<br />\n改善封鎖功能嘅好處係唔需要Admin介入定奪<br />\n亦都冇滅聲嘅爭議 有興趣可以去站務台推下小弟的post<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n[拋磚] 關於封鎖功能嘅改善建議<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2192442\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/2192442</a>"},{"pid":"ded8f238e44932647f8d34813d84e024643bb85c","tid":2192724,"uid":161684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:03:25.000Z","msg":"Push<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24a0093dec1ef4a566bc262a6bd7663e769f575d","tid":2192724,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-07T10:04:35.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"eca2c5664e